    "description_long": "This is a robust, rectangular yellow newspaper stand commonly found in urban environments. The main body is made of metal, featuring a large transparent display window on the front, showcasing a newspaper behind a protective pane. The upper section has a pull-down door with a lock and a clearly labeled 'PULL' instruction, as well as a coin slot for payment. Graffiti and stickers are visible on several sides, adding to its urban character. The base is reinforced with metal feet for stability, and the overall structure is designed to withstand outdoor conditions.",
